title: US Highest and Lowest Average Yearly Precipitation, USA,
name: US Highest and Lowest Average Yearly Precipitation, USA,
description: This dataset illustrates the highest and lowest average yearly precipitation in US cities.  A value of -1 means that the data is not applicable.  Also included are the rankings, the inverse rankings to be used for mapping purposes only, the city and state, the population, and the average precipitation in inches.            Source:  City-Data      URL:  http://www.city-data.com/top2/c462.html      http://www.city-data.com/top2/c463.html      Date Accessed:  November 9, 2007
